{
  "stem": "7683.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Russians stopped next to Warsaw, next to-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't go further for six months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That had happened this time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And right there, they-- they came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They want to bring all the Dutch soldiers, which were in Poland for-- somehow were prisoners or whatever-- to bring them back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we hear about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I pretended I am Dutch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't talk, because my Dutch-- I didn't have any Dutch living here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- and with the child together-- and she talked with some Dutch Captain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she told them, I think, the situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he agreed to keep us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He took us on the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, we were the only-- I was the only one not Dutch that was on this boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because there was some other people who tried to get in, but couldn't get in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and our child died on the boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had-- I don't know-- the food or whatever, food poisoning or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they was buried in the roof-- in-- in the-- an ocean by the Greek-- by Greece.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, we came to-- to-- Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in Marseilles, there-- there was-- they gave us through un-lousing, they called it-- folded everything, changing everything, because they were afraid of bringing so many sicknesses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, by train-- oh-- before that happened, we were three months in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When we came from Lublin, we traveled by train to Odessa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, it was very slow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was three months it took us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We went through Bucharest, Romania, things like that, until we came in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in Odessa, they had a special camp for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there we were also about three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
